metadata.name: Totally
metadata.description:
[Totally](https://twitter.com/to_tal_ly) is the co-founder of [SUP](https://twitter.com/supdotxyz), a game developer and one of the original [Blitmap](https://www.blitmap.com/) artist.

[Listen to the interview](https://arweave.net/juU-14Fl3Y1rt7nJkeZrdGe4vNqT3KJirMQfCtABt30)

---

**About the project**  
Huweb3 are conversations with the actors of what we broadly call "web3", a photographic series with the goal of raising funds for public goods. All profits are distributed to Gitcoin and protocol guild.

[Learn more](https://huweb3.xyz/about)
